rdPress such as, plugins that don’t integrate with the menu system in a consistent way, incompatible themes, and the post editor. Although Ghost doesn''>WPTavern: Why WordPress Doesn’t Need to Fear Ghost, Yet</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/tablepress/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>TablePress</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=tablepress&amp;_wpnonce=fcc2a3f57e&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''TablePress''>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
